                "caption": "Figure 1:V-JEPA 2.1 unlocks high-quality dense features.We compute PCA on patch features extracted from the same image or video and map the top three components to RGB channels for both V-JEPA 2 (ViT-g) and V-JEPA 2.1 (ViT-G).\nOur novel V-JEPA 2.1 produces dense representations with strong spatial and temporal consistency, learning semantically coherent features where similar objects map to the same PCA components.",
