                "caption": "Figure 3:Influence of the context lossℒc​t​x\\mathcal{L}_{ctx}.We show PCA visualizations of the feature map representations learned with V-JEPA 2 and with a model trained using V-JEPA 2 plus ourℒc​t​x\\mathcal{L}_{ctx}loss.\nWhile V-JEPA features only show fragmented local spatial structure, explicitly supervising unmasked regions withℒc​t​x\\mathcal{L}_{ctx}leads to feature maps that exhibit coherent spatial structure. Similar semantic parts (e.g., heads of dogs, wheels of cars) are mapped to the same PCA components.",
